Package compiler.symboltable

package compiler.symboltable
Defines a SymbolTable which is used during compilation to keep track of information about different Symbols found in a high-level-language program. These Symbols have different Types and are defined by a regex that every Symbol of this Type matches.
Author:
Alex Mandelias
